title: OPI NLL54 California Raspberry

title: Fancy Nights By Jessica Simpson Eau De Parfum Spray for Women, 3.40-Fluid Ounce
description: Designed for Women. Fragrance introduced by Jessica Simpson in 2010. For casual use.When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: OPI Rally Pretty Pink Serena Collection NLS19
description: A Part of Serena Glam Slam Collection. Rally Pretty Pink has a rosy pink base packed with pink and gold foil micro-glitter. The gold is very predominant in this shade and it really pops under the shatter but the pink is definitely noticeable. On the nail, the two colors combine to create a peachy duo-chrome effect.
